{"tid":1606890,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聽日 ，口號要升級。","createTime":"2019-09-30T16:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T18:10:24.000Z","uid":191392,"like":13,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"21f2bb00b2677ad30a94e18e92a3127f743cc467","tid":1606890,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:24:58.000Z","msg":"當聽日開始嘅時候，亦都係口號再轉嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n五年前，光復香港，時代革命看似遙遠，但五年後嘅今日，我地再無退路。 <br />\n<br />\n一係贏，一係面臨比新疆更恐怖嘅酷刑。<br />\n<br />\n臨時議會已經組成，每個人都知道五大訴求已經不足以去改變一切，十月一號，我地口號同時升級，我相信在座嘅香港兒女，手足，只要有人肯嗌，一定會有人接。<br />\n<br />\n黎明前嘅黑暗，係至撚黑暗。<br />\n願榮光歸香港。<br />\n<br />\n聽日國殤，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立</span>"},{"pid":"03500293a81724488ec1d52a4fc22b43464705a2","tid":1606890,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:25:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立</span>"},{"pid":"26bcfb042e8923206766853c795ea316f7238cb9","tid":1606890,"uid":191392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5xeSDN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5xeSDN.jpg&h=51db32f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc6f337b35e23193536f9e24f9251382194029e3","tid":1606890,"uid":191392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立</span>"},{"pid":"7aa0efb1f18139a69a81baed2c9188dbcb53db69","tid":1606890,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"86327deefcd99c554f97be53cbf4ddc2761bdebe","tid":1606890,"uid":191392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立</span>"},{"pid":"621b516a9dd1ee2435fab69bb98c4994cc02d6ee","tid":1606890,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"行動都一齊升級得唔得？<im